熊岭成立了自然保护区，成为了远近闻名的动物天堂。黑风、跳跳、袋鼠妈妈、洗刷刷、三只柯基、蕾蒂、嘎嘎、象奶奶这些马戏团老友们通过熊大的信来到保护区开始了新的生活，光头强成为了保护区的金牌导游，赵琳当上了保护区的义工。然而这时，新反派天才威和洞洞幺在森林里抓动物向王老板赚取科研经费。\r\n\r\n他甚至将魔爪伸向了白熊山的山神团子，建造地核能量提取仪，严重破坏了雪山的生态环境，威胁着狗熊岭的安全。为了对抗天才威，保护动物和森林，熊大、熊二、光头强、赵琳再度团结，深入森林，猛禽王国和雪山，历经千辛万苦，一次次挫败了天才威的诡计，终于战胜了天才威，停掉了地核机器，雪山又回到了往日的平静。","date":"2019-02-11","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/df/66/394412_vxrxQ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/df/66/394412_vxrxQ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/df/66/394412_vxrxQ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/df/66/394412_vxrxQ.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/df/66/394412_vxrxQ.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":7145,"total":51,"score":5.3,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":2,"4":9,"5":16,"6":20,"7":1,"8":1,"9":0,"10":1}},"tags":[{"name":"国产","count":17},{"name":"方特动漫","count":12},{"name":"TV","count":12},{"name":"童年","count":9},{"name":"搞笑","count":8},{"name":"中国","count":7},{"name":"原创","count":5},{"name":"治愈","count":5},{"name":"熊出没","count":5},{"name":"国漫","count":4},{"name":"2010-2019","count":4}],"eps":52,"collection":{"wish":7,"collect":92,"doing":3,"on_hold":3,"dropped":7}},{"id":439583,"type":2,"name":"Smash and Grab","name_cn":"粉碎与掠夺","summary":"　　After years of toiling away inside the engine room of a towering locomotive, two antiquated robots will risk everything for freedom and for each other.","date":"2019-02-11","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/37/1c/439583_XgX14.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/37/1c/439583_XgX14.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/37/1c/439583_XgX14.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/37/1c/439583_XgX14.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/37/1c/439583_XgX14.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":3,"score":6,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":1,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":2},{"name":"短片","count":1},{"name":"pixar","count":1}],"eps":0,"collection":{"wish":0,